    <briefdescription>
<para>This file implements the mixed mode display test where Stream1 is sourced from a live video input (AVPG pattern generator) and Stream2 is sourced from a non-live DMA frame buffer. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The two streams are alpha-blended and output through the DisplayPort interface.</para><para><preformatted>
MODIFICATION HISTORY:</preformatted></para><para><preformatted>Ver   Who  Date     Changes
